author: ate
msg: Fixing incorrect usage of ${portals.bridges.version} references which is unknown to the maven-plugin, and it should remain so
(there isn't such a thing like a "general" portals.bridges.version, only separate components each with their own version).
These incorrect references resulted in unsatisfied portals-bridges-common-.jar and portals-bridges-velocity-.jar error message
reported from maven-1 builds for custom portal projects generated with j2:portal.genapp (as the maven-plugin can't filter these variables).
